Ring UI: development environment setup

1. Install node.js

2: Install grunt-cli:

    npm install grunt -g

3. Install dependencies:

    npm install 

4. Prepare files:

    grunt

5. Start the watcher and the server:

    grunt server

=======================================

(Optional) Install VirtualBox and ievms to test run test on IE9+

    VirtualBox — https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
    ievms — https://github.com/xdissent/ievms#installation

Build production files

    grunt build

Clean generated files:

    grunt cleanup

Uninstall dependencies:

    grunt uninstall
